{"tid":2346190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太平山2˚C下雨起濃霧 可望降雪！","createTime":"2020-12-30T05:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:00:58.000Z","uid":131913,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec0e27e6b54d238b10a33814b9d734410702fbc","tid":2346190,"uid":131913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"【跨年急凍】太平山2˚C下雨起濃霧 可望降雪！下午2時後禁入園<br />\n<br />\n宜蘭太平山國家森林遊樂區介於海拔365至2000公尺，冬季強烈寒流來臨，區內海拔1000公尺以上據點有機會下雪，此波強烈寒流南下，太平山溫度恐下探攝氏0度以下，林務局羅東林區管理處今天（30日）至明年（2021年）元旦，間會視道路結冰積雪情況，實施區內道路「宜專一線」預警性機動管制措施，確保遊客用路安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201230/HBSE2OXF75BHTOLX4JJLXWIHIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201230%2FHBSE2OXF75BHTOLX4JJLXWIHIY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=0c36d126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201230%2FHBSE2OXF75BHTOLX4JJLXWIHIY%2F&h=e6727252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201230/HBSE2OXF75BHTOLX4JJLXWIHIY/</a>"},{"pid":"b80a9df782d1f7f88314456148a6e9ea14ea2c1d","tid":2346190,"uid":378141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:50:20.000Z","msg":"屌以為係香港太平山"},{"pid":"05efc3b9c84d775b4732d753b1c2ceed692d1142","tid":2346190,"uid":226573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"屌你"},{"pid":"704a4f46df791b40e2905db595b8dff7c3f5c2c5","tid":2346190,"uid":126642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚訝咗一秒"},{"pid":"41edd917ee5cedf5ac7c10cf481a75e33a82094b","tid":2346190,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:00:58.000Z","msg":"屌那星出面咁好太陽都有雪？<br />\n睇多兩睇，原來唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}